...lay your large hands, overlapping mine.

17
00:06:10,558 --> 00:06:16,358
失いたくないと願うほど
The more I pray not to lose you...

18
00:06:17,058 --> 00:06:22,508
苦しくなっていたの
...the more painful it became.

19
00:06:23,258 --> 00:06:29,508
唇についた 真っ赤な愛が
The crimson love upon my lips...

20
00:06:30,058 --> 00:06:36,508
消える前に あなたに会いたくて
...before it fades, I wanted to see you.

21
00:06:37,058 --> 00:06:42,958
目を閉じると 巻き戻される
When I close my eyes, I'm taken back...

22
00:06:43,558 --> 00:06:49,008
最後の温かい夜
...to that last warm night.

23
00:06:50,058 --> 00:06:56,558
優しいその目と 優しさと
Those kind eyes and that kindness...

24
00:06:57,058 --> 00:07:03,008
言葉すべて 嘘じゃないと言いかせて
...tell me that all those words weren't lies.

25
00:07:03,558 --> 00:07:09,558
これで最後の恋だと思うの
I think this will be my last love.

26
00:07:10,058 --> 00:07:16,008
だから繋ぎ止めていたかったのに
That's why I wanted to hold on to you, and yet...

27
00:07:30,058 --> 00:07:35,508
もうすべてわかってるから
Since I've understood everything now...

28
00:07:36,058 --> 00:07:42,008
もう私に近寄らないでよ
Don't get close to me anymore.

29
00:07:43,058 --> 00:07:49,508
果てしないこの 苦しみまでも愛せるほど
I can love even the suffering of this endless child...

30
00:07:50,058 --> 00:07:56,508
強い人はいないから
...because there is no one as strong as you.

31
00:08:00,058 --> 00:08:06,508
あなたを愛しているから
