It feels pretty good.

401
00:33:44,548 --> 00:33:46,048
タンバリンにしようかな。
Maybe I'll go with a tambourine.

402
00:33:46,048 --> 00:33:47,048
タンバリンね。
Tambourine, huh.

403
00:33:47,048 --> 00:33:48,048
タンバリンで。
With a tambourine.

404
00:33:48,048 --> 00:33:49,048
